<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Joseph_Smith" title="Joseph Smith">Smith, Joseph</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://byustudies.byu.edu/further-study-lesson/volume-3-chapter-2/">"Chapter 2"</a>. In <a href="/wiki/B._H._Roberts" title="B. H. Roberts">Roberts, B. H.</a> (ed.). <i><a href="/wiki/History_of_the_Church_(Joseph_Smith)" class="mw-redirect" title="History of the Church (Joseph Smith)">History of the Church</a>, Volume 3</i>. p.&#160;18<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">18 August</span> 2021</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Chapter+2&amp;rft.btitle=History+of+the+Church%2C+Volume+3&amp;rft.pages=18&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbyustudies.byu.edu%2Ffurther-study-lesson%2Fvolume-3-chapter-2%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWord+of+Wisdom+%28Latter+Day+Saints%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
